title: 3 Bedroom Manufactured Home
posting_body: Just looking for a place to call home?
Look no further thank Oakland Glens.
Our community is conveniently located on the Novi and Walled lake border giving you easy access to all the fun both have to offer.
Not to mention all the awesome amenities right here in the community!
Oakland Glens is currently in the process  of getting this 2016 3bedroom 2 bathroom home with 1056 square feet of space ready to be you new home!
So reach out today and let us help you get the process started!
Photos are stock photography/ Options and colors may vary.
